# Aether Agent Rules

## Critical — Never Change
- WebRTC data channel: ordered: false, maxRetransmits: 0
- CC11 breath control: always callbackRef, never useState
- Oscilloscope canvas: height: 180, flexShrink: 0 — do not override
- localStorage keys: jamlink_user / jamlink_theme — do not rename
- Git commits: always --no-verify to bypass Husky

## Git Staging Rules
- NEVER use `git add -A` unless explicitly instructed
- Always stage only the specific files you changed: `git add path/to/file1 path/to/file2`
- Before every commit, run `git status` and confirm only intended files are staged
- If unexpected files appear in `git status`, stop and report them — do not commit
- Only use `git add -A` when the task explicitly says "stage all changes"

## Token Rules
- No hardcoded hex values anywhere — all colours from design-tokens.ts
- No hardcoded px values — all spacing from layout tokens
- Theme tokens use keys: purple, pink, green, blue (in that order for players 1–4)
- Import theme map from theme-map.ts, not directly from themeTokens by name

## Vendor Copy Rules
- DS changes made in vendor/ must be manually cp'd back to DesignSystem source
- Never run cp commands automatically — always report which files need copying
- Token file lives at vendor/DesignSystem/src/tokens/design-tokens.ts

## Component Rules
- Inline styles only — no CSS files, no Tailwind
- TypeScript strict — zero tsc errors before any commit
- Follow existing DS component patterns for file structure and exports
